===Noun===
'''comparative''' (''plural:'' '''[[comparatives]]''')

# {{grammar}} A grammatical construction expressing the outcome of a comparison between two items; in English, formed by appending “[[-er]]” to the end of the adjective (for some short adjectives only) or putting “[[more]]” before it.
#: ''The comparative of “big” is “bigger”''

